<plot>TV's former "Barney Fife", Don Knotts, hosted this variety show that contained a bit of music, but mostly comedy skits and sketches featuring Knotts, guest stars and a talented supporting cast. One regular bit was called "The Front Porch", which consisted of Knotts and that week's guest rocking on a porch and talking.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?553999</url></doc>
